This is the README file for the MAGNETOCOSMIC code written by L.Desorgher under the Septimess project

-Dependence
------------
	-The Geant4 toolkit should be installed (http://wwwasd.web.cern.ch/wwwasd/geant4/geant4.html)
	

-Compilation and installation
------------------------------
-1)From the MAGNETOCOSMICS main directory	type:
	./configure_and_build.sh 
-2)In the bash (tcl) shell  startup file (probably .bashrc) you should add :
	"source magcos_dir/setupMAGNETOCOSMICS.sh"
   where magcos_dir define the directory where MAGNETOCOSMICS is installed
   
-Use of the code
------------------

	MAGNETOCOSMICS <macro_file>.
 	If the parameter  macro_file is not provided the code is used in  interactive mode.
   
-Examples
----------
Some examples are contained in the directory examples.
		 
-Documentation
--------------
The document   doc/magnetocosmics_sum.pdf represents 
the user guide of the code.  
